Usage: set_path_adjust [-help] <adjust_value>
                       -path_adjust_group <path_adjust_group_name>
                       -view <string> [-setup | -hold ]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
<adjust_value>             # Value of slack adjustment (float, required)
-hold                      # Specifies adjust value for early paths
                           # (bool, optional)
-path_adjust_group <path_adjust_group_name>
                           # The name of path adjust group which specifies the
                           # path for which the adjustment will be applied
                           # (string, required)
-setup                     # Specifies adjust value for late paths
                           # (bool, optional)
-view <string>             # Specifies the view for which adjustment will be
                           # applied (string, required)